subject: Sports Injuries
Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: A 10-minute break by Victoria Azarenka during her match with Sloane Stephens at the Australian Open shifted momentum and added fuel to a debate over the legitimacy of medical timeouts.
